Package ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.core.api

Class SequentialActionSupplier<T,R,THIS extends SequentialActionSupplier<T,R,THIS>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.tinkoff.qa.neptune.core.api.SequentialActionSupplier<T,R,THIS>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - is the type of an input value.
    R - is the type of a value which is supposed to be used by some action.
    THIS - is self-type. It is necessary for andThen(String, Function, Object...) and andThen(String, Object, Object...) methods.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.function.Supplier<java.util.function.Consumer<T>>

    public abstract class SequentialActionSupplier<T,R,THIS extends SequentialActionSupplier<T,R,THIS>>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.function.Supplier<java.util.function.Consumer<T>>
    This class is designed to restrict actions to perform on certain values. Also it restricts chains of actions. It is supposed to supply chains of similar actions.
